01:13:22,440 --> 01:13:23,440
Itu dia.

870
01:13:24,234 --> 01:13:25,860
<i>Jawab jika kau bisa dengar.</i>

871
01:13:33,284 --> 01:13:35,161
<i>Bisa periksa ruang peladen?</i>

872
01:13:36,746 --> 01:13:38,623
<i>Menuju ke sana.</i>

873
01:13:39,207 --> 01:13:41,292
